id3mtag (0.81-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * All present tags are now updated by default (i.e. ID3v2, Lyrics3)
  * Add support for POPM frames (popularity counters) in ID3v2
  * Added support for --list-genres
  * Bug fixes

 -- Marc R. Schoolderman <info@squell.net>  Fri, 30 Jun 2023 16:30:12 +0100

id3mtag (0.80-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * ID3v2.4 support added: upon writing, will be converted to ID3v2.3
  * Added support for --long-options
  * Added complete tag viewing by using -v/--verbose
  * Added programmable bash completion
  * Bug fixes to handling of COMM/TXXX frames in ID3v2

 -- Marc R. Schoolderman <squell@alumina.nl>  Sun, 20 Dec 2015 23:51:44 +0100

id3mtag (0.79-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Added tag viewing
  * Will now read/write ID3v2 tags by default if already present
  * Support for reading non-standard ID3v2 frames using %{XXXX}
  * Minor bug fixes

 -- Marc R. Schoolderman <squell@alumina.nl>  Thu, 29 Jan 2015 18:17:23 +0100

id3mtag (0.78-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Added support for Lyrics3 v2 tags
  * Added -E to only process existing tags
  * Added word splitting (%*) in substitution
  * Other minor changes

 -- Marc R. Schoolderman <squell@alumina.nl>  Tue, 21 Mar 2006 09:25:33 +0100

id3mtag (0.77-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Added support for ID3v2.2 tags and Unicode inside ID3v2 tags.
  * Added -M to preserve file timestamps
  * Added -D to copy tags between files
  * Added selection in string substitution ("%||?")

 -- Marc R. Schoolderman <squell@alumina.nl>  Tue, 31 Jan 2006 18:16:58 +0100

id3mtag (0.76-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Added -m switch for shorthand tagging (-m "%a.mp3" == -a %1 "*.mp3")
  * Added -R switch for GNU find-like recursive searching
  * Fixed some cases of ID3v2 tag rejection

 -- Marc R. Schoolderman <squell@alumina.nl>  Wed, 20 Jul 2005 22:44:40 +0200

id3mtag (0.75-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * First Debianization; see `CHANGES' for further history.

